## Category Placement Guidelines

Categories are updated weekly.

### New Releases

- All games with a 1+ star rating receive a New Release tag.
- **3 Stars** - Prioritized placement in *featured* and top positioning.
- **2 Stars** - May appear in weekly releases if space allows, otherwise placed lower.
- **1 Star** - Always placed at the bottom of New Releases, unless sorted by Newest.

### Burst Games

- Priority given to 3-star games.
- 2-star games may appear if popularity drives demand.

### Stake Exclusives

- Priority given to 3-star games.
- 2-star games may appear if driven by popularity.
